name: Donatello_Urban_Style_Solid_Wood_Leatherette_Padded_Parson_Chair_(Set_of_2)
reviews: The chairs look good for the price and the material seems durable.
These don't assemble easily. The screw holes do not line up and you have to remove and replace the lining and it never lines up right.
description:
Get the rich look of leather without worrying about cleaning and
conditioning with these Donatello dining chairs. Beautiful high
back and set features a stunning design with deep comfort
seating.The faux leather recreates the look of real leather. To
coordinate with the faux leather, the frame and legs are
constructed of solid wood finished in espresso. These chairs work
well as compact dining chairs or as game chairs for any room. This
set of two armless side chairs feature contemporary faux leather
for comfort and a high back height for support. The seat and back
are padded with high-density foam for great comfortable feeling.
